Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.13,0:01:08.92,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)}{\bord0.1\blur15\be7\3c&000000\3a&66}而後結為伴侶
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.42,0:01:12.64,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\bord0.1\blur15\be7\3c&000000\3a&66}作品中講述的故事
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.64,0:01:15.18,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)}{\bord0.1\blur15\be7\3c&000000\3a&66}終究與現實不同
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.31,0:01:21.94,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\bord0.1\blur15\be7\3c&000000\3a&66}常言道，兄妹起初不是陌路
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.02,0:01:24.52,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\bord0.1\blur15\be7\3c&000000\3a&66}可繼兄妹對彼此而言
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.52,0:01:26.27,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\bord0.1\blur15\be7\3c&000000\3a&66}起初是外人
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.27,0:01:29.69,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)}{\bord0.1\blur15\be7\3c&000000\3a&66}歲月蹉跎後仍是外人
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.82,0:02:53.32,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}老爸決定再婚了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.74,0:02:58.45,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}對方在上司帶我去過的店裡工作
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.45,0:03:01.49,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}還照顧過喝得爛醉的我
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.49,0:03:03.66,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}你該不會被騙了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.04,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}放心吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.50,0:03:07.63,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}亞季子絕對不是那種人
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.46,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}你今晚見到她就明白了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.01,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}今晚?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.76,0:03:14.30,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}好燙
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.97,0:03:17.39,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&333333\4c&333333}大家見個面
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.39,0:03:18.80,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&333333\4c&333333}時間定在你打工結束後
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.60,0:03:23.31,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}又搞突然襲擊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.19,0:03:31.57,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2}{\3c&4C4C4C\4c&4C4C4C}真的準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.40,0:03:31.15,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\bord2}{\3c&4C4C4C\4c&4C4C4C}好燙好燙
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.53,0:03:36.57,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}你說什麼?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.57,0:03:37.41,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}沒什麼
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.99,0:03:39.57,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}好燙
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.57,0:03:41.87,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}只要老爸過得幸福就行了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.54,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}我還是和以前一樣
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.33,0:03:47.04,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}不能和以前一樣了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.50,0:03:49.04,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}你有妹妹了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.21,0:03:51.09,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}妹妹?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.54,0:03:53.09,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}沒錯，妹妹
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.63,0:03:55.01,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}亞季子的女兒
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.10,0:04:06.35,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}初次見面
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.35,0:04:08.27,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}我是綾瀨亞季子
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.27,0:04:11.56,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}不好意思，把忙著打工的你叫了出來
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.40,0:04:13.69,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}沒關係
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.65,0:04:16.82,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}我是他兒子，淺村悠太
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.24,0:04:21.20,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&312E4C\4c&312E4C}{\bord2.5}妳也來打聲招呼
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.28,0:04:24.08,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&312E4C\4c&312E4C}{\bord2.5}初次見面
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.08,0:04:25.41,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&312E4C\4c&312E4C}{\bord2.5}我是綾瀨沙季
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.29,0:04:28.16,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&665850\4c&665850}{\bord2.5}老爸
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.88,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&665850\4c&665850}{\bord2.5}沙季和你一樣大
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.42,0:04:34.96,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&665850\4c&665850}{\bord2.5}今年17歲，讀高二
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.59,0:04:39.18,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&665850\4c&665850}{\bord2.5}不過你的生日比她早一週
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.18,0:04:41.76,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&665850\4c&665850}{\bord2.5}抱歉讓你誤會了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.76,0:04:44.14,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&665850\4c&665850}{\bord2.5}沙季這孩子長大後，就完全不讓我拍照了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.14,0:04:46.47,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}沙季這孩子長大後，就完全不讓我拍照了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.47,0:04:50.65,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}我的眼神看著有些兇，不上鏡
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.11,0:04:55.78,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&274766\4c&274766}不過我終於放心了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.40,0:05:00.32,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}畢竟是要一起生活的人
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.32,0:05:03.28,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}我之前還擔心對方會不會很可怕
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.37,0:05:06.87,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}這可不好說
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.87,0:05:09.91,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}真正可怕的人也會擺出和顏悅色的模樣
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.58,0:05:12.67,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&202B34\4c&202B34}聽說你每天都在打工
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.67,0:05:15.17,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&202B34\4c&202B34}為上大學積攢學費
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.17,0:05:17.80,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&202B34\4c&202B34}成績也非常優秀
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.80,0:05:20.34,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&202B34\4c&202B34}高智商罪犯也不在少數
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.52,0:05:31.31,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}對了，趁媽媽他們還沒出來
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.31,0:05:34.11,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}我有些話想跟你說
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.11,0:05:35.69,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}不能對父母說嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.69,0:05:36.57,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}是的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.57,0:05:39.94,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}乾脆挑明，那些話只能跟你說
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.49,0:05:44.45,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}這點時間就得到妳的信任了嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.03,0:05:46.37,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3.5}我真厲害啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.46,0:05:51.71,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3.5}你的幽默
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.29,0:05:53.33,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&475C66\4c&475C66}{\bord2.5}談吐
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.83,0:05:54.96,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&475C66\4c&475C66}{\bord2.5}還有表情
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.46,0:05:58.30,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}都讓人感受不到熱情
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.21,0:06:00.42,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.5}所以
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.13,0:06:05.22,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3.5}或許你能理解我的話
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.94,0:06:20.40,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}我對你不抱有任何期待
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.32,0:06:24.11,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}也希望你不要對我抱有期待
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.70,0:06:30.87,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}你應該能理解，我在說什麼吧
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.96,0:06:39.21,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&1A1A1A\4c&1A1A1A}我放心了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.26,0:06:43.42,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}終於放心了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.18,0:06:45.34,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\3c&333333\4c&333333}從這一刻起
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.02,0:06:53.85,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}嗯，我也是
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.60,0:06:56.15,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}從這一刻起
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.06,0:06:59.98,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}我們以後就這樣相處吧，綾瀨
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.49,0:07:04.36,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0}謝謝你，淺村
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.83,0:07:12.79,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&333333\4c&333333}悠太
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.70,0:07:16.17,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&333333\4c&333333}你知道除臭劑放在哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.62,0:07:17.92,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&333333\4c&333333}電視機旁邊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.38,0:07:20.84,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&333333\4c&333333}你昨天給窗簾用過，之後一直放在那
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.92,0:07:22.80,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&333333\4c&333333}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.42,0:07:25.38,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\bord3}{\3c&352C4C\4c&352C4C}謝了
